inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let systemName = "license-management";
let dataset=requests
    // additional filters can be applied here
    | where client_Type != "Browser"
    | where (iif(itemType == "request", (column_ifexists('customDimensions', '')["system_SystemName"] == systemName), (itemType == "request" and column_ifexists("id", operation_ParentId) in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == systemName
        | distinct id))) 
        or (itemType != "request" and operation_ParentId in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == systemName
        | distinct id)))));
dataset
// change 'operation_Name' on the below line to segment by a different property
| summarize Count=sumif(itemCount, (iif(itemType == "request", (column_ifexists('customDimensions', '')["system_SystemName"] == systemName), (itemType == "request" and column_ifexists("id", operation_ParentId) in ((requests
    | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == systemName
    | distinct id))) 
    or (itemType != "request" and operation_ParentId in ((requests
    | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == systemName
    | distinct id)))))), Avg = avg(duration), Percentiles_95 = percentiles(duration, 95)
    by operation_Name
// calculate duration percentiles and count for all requests (overall)
| union(dataset
    | summarize Count=sumif(itemCount, (iif(itemType == "request", (column_ifexists('customDimensions', '')["system_SystemName"] == systemName), (itemType == "request" and column_ifexists("id", operation_ParentId) in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == systemName
        | distinct id))) 
        or (itemType != "request" and operation_ParentId in ((requests
        | where customDimensions["system_SystemName"] == systemName
        | distinct id)))))), Avg = avg(duration), Percentiles_95 = percentiles(duration, 95)
    | extend operation_Name="Overall")
| order by Percentiles_95
| where Percentiles_95 > 500
